Package: RefiLlama
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive DeFiLlama API Client for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("James", "Chapman", , "jchapman@bankofcanada", role = c("aut","cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3154-9699"))
Description: A comprehensive R client for the DeFiLlama API that provides access to
    DeFi protocol data including Total Value Locked (TVL), cryptocurrency prices,
    trading volumes, fees, revenue, and yield farming information. Supports both
    legacy API endpoints and the new Pro API for enhanced functionality.
